---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Justin Spidell — background, skills, and what I'm working on."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl">About</h1>
    <div class="prose mt-10" style="color: var(--color-muted);">
      <p>
        I'm Justin Spidell, a software developer based online at
        <a href="https://justin.spidell.org">justin.spidell.org</a>. I like building tools that
        are fast, understandable, and pleasant to maintain.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl" style="color: var(--color-fg);">What I work with</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>TypeScript, Astro, and modern front-end tooling</li>
        <li>CLI tools and automation</li>
        <li>Data visualization and exploratory interfaces</li>
        <li>Homelab infrastructure and scripting</li>
      </ul>
      <h2 class="text-2xl" style="color: var(--color-fg);">Currently</h2>
      <p>
        Shipping this personal site, writing on the blog, and replacing placeholder project entries
        with real work. Reach me via the <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
